thread.title: Twelve tourists dead in Odessa

author: eTN Managing Editor
title: Twelve tourists dead in Odessa
text:
Twelve tourists dead in Odessa   
Oct 17, 2015 eTN   
Ukraine's holiday region near Odessa meant death to 12 tourists on a fishing excursion. 
No life jackets and going into dangerous water despite weather warnings. 
At least 12 people have been killed after a ship taking passengers back from a fishing trip sank.
